    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001230/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """Thermodynamics has three objectives for the training of an engineer:
Carry out energy balances to open systems undegoing physical processes (conservation of energy, First Law)
Analyse the quality of the energy flows in processes, either in terms of entropy or exergy (degradation of energy, Second Law)
Calculate thermophysical properties in systems with changes in composition: pure substances, mixtures, multiphase systems (vapour-liquid), reactive systems, etc.
This subject develops the concepts and tools required for calculating energy and exergy (entropy) balances in processes involving open systems with pure substances, mixtures, chemical reactions, etc that reach thermodynamic equilibrium.
The structure of the subject is developed based on three underlying pillars: Principles, Properties and Processes, which are applied to/calculated for open systems, i.e., those that exchange energy and mass with their surrounding."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/cr.arnaiz%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/cr.arnaiz%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/ignacio.lopez%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Ampliacion de Termodinamica"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001230/2025-26/%28a%29> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "(a)" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "APLICA. Habilidad para aplicar conocimientos científicos, matemáticos y tecnológicos en sistemas relacionados con la práctica de la ingeniería."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001230/2025-26/%28c%29> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "(c)" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "DISEÑA. Habilidad para diseñar un sistema, componente o proceso que alcance los requisitos deseados teniendo en cuenta restricciones realistas tales como las económicas, medioambientales, sociales, políticas, éticas, de salud y seguridad, de fabricación y de sostenibilidad."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001230/2025-26/%28e%29> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "(e)" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "RESUELVE. Habilidad para identificar, formular y resolver problemas de ingeniería."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001230/2025-26/%28h%29> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "(h)" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "ENTIENDE LOS IMPACTOS. Educación amplia necesaria para entender el impacto de las soluciones ingenieriles en un contexto social global."@es .

