<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001230/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The heterogeneity of the student's background may require adaptation of the syllabus and evaluation methods. Progressive evaluation (PE) will be carried during lectures, individually.
Their form, content and timing will be adapted to how the subject develops.
Progressive evaluation (PE) activities will add up to two (2) points to the final exam
A minimum grade of 4 must be attained in the Final Exam to add the averaged Progressive evaluation (PE) results to the final grade."""@es ;
